Supported Host OSes: Ubuntu 32 and 64-bit 10.04 and onwards. 
Other Linux distributions may work too, but not they are tested.

Supported Guests:
Architecture: i386
OS: Windows XP, Windows 7, Linux 

1. First install dependent packages:
   zlib1g-dev, libglib2.0-dev, binutils-dev
   freeglut3-dev (or libsdl1.2-dev)

   $ sudo apt-get install zlib1g-dev libglib2.0-dev binutils-dev
   freeglut3-dev

2. Build DECAF
   $ ./configure & make

3. Build a plugin:
   $ cd /path/to/plugin
   $ ./configure --decaf-path=/path/to/decaf
   $ make
